{"tid":2012042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★ 赤柱監獄謀殺犯與販毒犯打鬥　1人受傷送院","createTime":"2020-05-11T11:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T11:51:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c004f7d6f6fe59c56b75269fb9e84f348353bf26","tid":2012042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"赤柱監獄懲教人員今日（11日）公布，制止一名還押在囚人士襲擊另一名還押在囚人士。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今早約7時40分，一名52歲男性在囚人士在運動場內，襲擊另一名27歲男性在囚人士。在場懲教人員見狀立即制止施襲者，並召喚支援人員到場。事件中，受襲在囚人士頭部受傷，經院所醫生檢查及治理後被送往公立醫院作進一步診治。施襲者則並無受傷。<br />\n<br />\n事件已轉交警方調查，懲教署稱，兩名在囚人士分別因販運危險藥物罪及謀殺罪而被還押。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2640009/赤柱監獄謀殺犯與販毒犯打鬥%E3%80%801人受傷送院?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2640009%2F%E8%B5%A4%E6%9F%B1%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E7%8A%AF%E8%88%87%E8%B2%A9%E6%AF%92%E7%8A%AF%E6%89%93%E9%AC%A5%25E3%2580%25801%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E5%82%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=7226d447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2640009/赤柱監獄謀殺犯與販毒犯打鬥%E3%80%801人受傷送院?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"cf076ad73a2bb3a94ccf2c788cb7f42ee95c2d6d","tid":2012042,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87d69fd1468525bd51b22b829e9c280dcdfd14f","tid":2012042,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime